  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "61e91b3aaff09e000066fdfe",
      "text": "(2.3.2.1-2) Metaphor of hiking",
      "created": 1548927356,
      "updated": 1553661404,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b3aaff09e000066fdff",
      "text": "",
      "created": 1548927356,
      "updated": 1548927356,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b3aaff09e000066fe00",
      "text": "Let's imagine the hiking in the mountain path.",
      "created": 1548927356,
      "updated": 1548927356,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b3aaff09e000066fe01",
      "text": "",
      "created": 1548927356,
      "updated": 1548927356,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b3aaff09e000066fe02",
      "text": "[https://gyazo.com/ecbb06a79da7bac43fee8fc6c1527bfb]",
      "created": 1548927356,
      "updated": 1548927356,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b3aaff09e000066fe03",
      "text": "Left: Goal is far, Right: Make a subgoal, a resting place, nearby",
      "created": 1548927356,
      "updated": 1548927382,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b3aaff09e000066fe04",
      "text": "",
      "created": 1548927356,
      "updated": 1548927356,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b3aaff09e000066fe05",
      "text": "When the goal is far away, you want to take a break soon, especially when there is a hard slope. However, if you know that there is a resting place on the way up the slope? Even if the top of the mountain is still far away, you feel that you can keep trying hard.",
      "created": 1548927356,
      "updated": 1548927386,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b3aaff09e000066fe06",
      "text": "",
      "created": 1548927356,
      "updated": 1548927356,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b3aaff09e000066fe07",
      "text": "[Timeboxing] works very similar. For example, if you declare to yourself that \"I do X for the next 25 minutes\" and start the timer, even if that task becomes painful in ten minutes, you can keep working thinking that \"if I try hard for the next 15 minutes it is over\". If you start the task X as for today's task, when it gets hard, you may escape to other tasks â€” for example, checking emails, taking care of colleagues kindly, going to the bathroom.",
      "created": 1548927356,
      "updated": 1548927392,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b3aaff09e000066fe08",
      "text": "",
      "created": 1548927356,
      "updated": 1548927356,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b3aaff09e000066fe09",
      "text": "The escaped people justify their choice, saying as follows:",
      "created": 1548927356,
      "updated": 1548927396,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b3aaff09e000066fe0a",
      "text": "",
      "created": 1548927356,
      "updated": 1548927356,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b3aaff09e000066fe0b",
      "text": "\tChecking mail is part of my work.",
      "created": 1548927356,
      "updated": 1548927356,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b3aaff09e000066fe0c",
      "text": "\tIt is necessary for work to help colleagues.",
      "created": 1548927356,
      "updated": 1548927356,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b3aaff09e000066fe0d",
      "text": "\tGoing to the bathroom is physiological desire so it cannot avoid",
      "created": 1548927356,
      "updated": 1549168848,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b3aaff09e000066fe0e",
      "text": "",
      "created": 1548927356,
      "updated": 1548927356,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b3aaff09e000066fe0f",
      "text": "However, observing from the viewpoint of others, it seems to escape in 10 minutes from a hard task and to do other things. It is [procrastination] by creating an urgent task themselves, and takes time from an important task.",
      "created": 1548927356,
      "updated": 1548927403,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b3aaff09e000066fe10",
      "text": "",
      "created": 1548927356,
      "updated": 1548927356,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b3aaff09e000066fe11",
      "text": "To avoid the procrastination, setting the visible goal by [timeboxing] is useful.",
      "created": 1548927356,
      "updated": 1549167087,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b3aaff09e000066fe12",
      "text": "",
      "created": 1548927356,
      "updated": 1548927356,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b3aaff09e000066fe13",
      "text": "",
      "created": 1548927356,
      "updated": 1548927356,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b3aaff09e000066fe14",
      "text": "[en.icon]",
      "created": 1553661404,
      "updated": 1553661404,
